_sText:
de_MkZk_Grabenkrieg_v1

Bomb/defuse-map build similar to real WW1-trench-systems.

T's
Spawn: within the no-mans-land.
Objective: storm the trenches, clear the bunkers and blow them up.

CT's
Spawn: inside the trenches supply-sections.
Objective: defend bunker A and B.

Both teams have an adustable artillery-gun near their spawns for indirect fire.

(I think it is not so well balanced and with bots its hard to test since they seem to not understand the concept of trench-warfare. So i would be glad to hear feedback for improvements!)
